CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Skye Bioscience Inc is a pre-clinical pharmaceutical company located in San Diego, California. It researches and develops and plans to commercialize cannabinoid derivatives through its own directed research efforts and through several license agreements with the University of Mississippi. The company's lead compound, SBI-100, is initially being developed to treat ocular disease.
